  "text": "Quantitation of genomic 5me C content by high-pressure liquid chromatography-tandem mass spectrometry. The overall 5me C (5-methyl-2 ¶-deoxycytidine) content [as percentage of total 2 ¶-deoxycytidine (2dC) content] in genomic and control DNAs was determined by a highpressure liquid chromatography/tandem mass spectrometry (LC-MS/MS) procedure as described elsewhere [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , with minor modifications. Please see supplementary materials for a detailed description.",
